<link href="/survey.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all"/>
	<div class="main-container">
			<div class="header-container">
			<p>The survey below has a number of words that describe different feelings and emotions.Read each word and then mark the appropriate answer in the space to the right of that word. Reflecting back on your last interaction in todayâ€™s experiment, indicate to what extent that interaction made you feel in the following way.</p><br/>
			
			<p>Use the following scale to record your answers:</p><br/>
			<p>(1) Not at all, (2) a little, (3) moderately, (4) quite a bit, (5) extremely.</p> 
			
			</div>
			<table>
			<%i=0%>
		      <%@survey.each do |survey|%>
		      <%i+=1%>
		      <%if i%2 == 1%>
		      <tr>
		      <%end%>
				<td><%=survey%></td>
				<td>
				<label>1</label>
				<input type="radio" id=<%="very_slightly_#{i}"%> title="Very Slightly" value="1" name=<%="user_#{i}_option"%>><label for="user_option" class="light"></label>
        		<input type="radio" id=<%="little_#{i}"%> title="Little" value="2" name=<%="user_#{i}_option"%>><label for="user_option" class="light"></label>
        		<input type="radio" id=<%="moderately_#{i}"%> title="Moderately" value="3" name=<%="user_#{i}_option"%>><label for="user_option" class="light"></label>
        		<input type="radio" id=<%="quite_a_bity_#{i}"%> title="Quite a bit" value="4" name=<%="user_#{i}_option"%>><label for="user_option" class="light"></label>
        		<input type="radio" id=<%="extremely_#{i}"%> title="Extremely" value="5" name=<%="user_#{i}_option"%>><label for="user_option" class="light"></label>
				<label>5</label>
				</td>
				<%if i % 2 ==0%>
			  </tr>
			  <%end%>
		      <%end%>
			</table>
			
			<div class="footer-area">
			<button class="submit" id="okbutton"  value="submit" type="button">OK</button>
			
			</div>
			
			
			
    </div>
<% @current_controller = "survey" %>
<%= render :partial => "shared/controllerinfo" %>
